data.description: This 3-bed, 2-bath brick home in Rusk, Texas is located in a convenient neighborhood close to town. Perfect for a family or a great investment opportunity. It's currently rented for $1,250/month. With a new roof and upgrades, maintenance is easy. Fenced back yard and concrete drive. Contact your favorite realtor for details and a showing!
